---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Blog & Insights
description: Technical articles, industry news, and regulatory updates from Acme Chemicals' team of chemical experts.
permalink: /blog/
---

<div class="page-header">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="breadcrumb">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <span>/</span>
      <span>Blog</span>
    </div>
    <h1>Insights from Our Lab to Yours</h1>
    <p class="lead">Deep technical dives, regulatory updates, and industry trends from Acme Chemicals' scientists and engineers.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="card-grid">
      {% for post in collections.blog %}
      <article class="card">
        <div class="card-image">
          <img src="{{ post.data.image }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }}" loading="lazy">
        </div>
        <div class="card-content">
          <span class="card-tag">{{ post.data.category }}</span>
          <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
          <p>{{ post.data.excerpt }}</p>
          <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-top: auto;">
            <span style="font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--color-text-muted);">{{ post.date | dateFormat }}</span>
            <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="card-link">Read Article</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Stay ahead of chemical industry trends</h2>
    <p>Subscribe to our monthly newsletter for regulatory updates, technical guides, and product innovations — delivered to your inbox.</p>
    <div class="cta-buttons">
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Subscribe to Newsletter</a>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-white btn-lg">Talk to an Expert</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
